Fast track service
After having been going through the triage, which will be done within 12 hours of you contacting us, if your pain does not resolve within provided time, you will be referred to a physiotherapist located near to you. Since the time of deciding you not being benefited throughself-management, your appointment for face to face assessment will be made within 12 hours, then your treatment will be completed within 4 weeks. Based upon treatment outcome

Standard service
After having been going through the triage, which will be done within 24 hours of you contacting us, if your pain does not resolve within provided time, you will be referred to a physiotherapist located near to you. Since the time of deciding you not being benefited through self-management, your appointment for face to face assessment will be made within 24 hours, then your treatment will be completed within 6-8 weeks. Based upon treatment outcome, further recommendations will be made.
